These are Puzzles for 4x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-1::.
There 6 different types of food: blueberry, cabbage, peach, pear, peas, radish
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, animation, comedy, disaster, martial-arts, thriller
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: february, january, may, december, july, april
The people have 6 different hobbies: sudoku, board-games, card-games, baking, cooking, drawing
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person watching comedy movies##2
 5. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person eating radish is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
14. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
15. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person eating peas##1
16. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Food          | radish   | blueberry     | cabbage | pear     | peach     | peas   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | martial-arts  | comedy  | thriller | animation | action |
| Birthday         | january | july | may | december    | february  | april |
| Hobby     | board-games     | baking    | sudoku    | cooking   | drawing      | card-games    |

