.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-2::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  librarian, journalist, security-guard, writer, scientist, entrepreneur
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, animation, disaster, mystery, scientific, zombie
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, irispy, iris, begonia, balloon-flower
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cricket, golf, parkour, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the security-guard##1
 4. the librarian is the person who growsirispy##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 6. the person watching action movies is on the right of the scientist##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the security-guard is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
12. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
13. the librarian is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is badminton##2
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the journalist and the person watching scientific movies##2
15. the security-guard is on the right of the writer##1
16. the person watching mystery movies is the journalist##1
17. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5     |     6     |
| Job          | journalist | writer  | security-guard       | librarian  | scientist   | entrepreneur |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | disaster     | scientific | zombie | animation | action    |
