.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, boat, quad-bike, tram, bike
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, board-games, gardening, photography, rock-climbing, woodworking
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, ferret, rabbit, snake, turtle
City: miami, marseilles, berlin, colone, paris, liverpool
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the person traveling to miami is between the person driving the jet-ski and the owner of the dog##2
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
11. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
14. the owner of the chinchilla is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
16. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |      5      |       6       |
| Transport   | boat  | quad-bike         | bike    | jet-ski      | tram    | airplane |
| Hobby      | gardening | rock-climbing | baking  | photography | board-games | woodworking   |
