.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-14::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, november, february, september, august, may
There are 6 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, indonesian, mexican, russian, thai
6 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, mouse, hedgehog, goldfish, bird
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the russian##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the russian##1
 5. the indonesian is on the left of the mexican##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person drinking 7up and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is between the egyptian and the person drinking iced-tea##2
13. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the bird##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
15. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the russian##1
16. the chinese is on the far left##1
17. the person drinking juice is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |     4     |     5      |     6      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | lemonade | coffee     | mirinda   | iced-tea   | juice      |
| Birthday   | may  | september   | february       | july   | august    | november |
| Nationality   | chinese | thai     | egyptian   | russian   | indonesian | mexican    |
| Pet     | cat | bird    | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse  | rabbit        |

