.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-15::.
House: wooden, craftsman, victorian, colonial, cottage, cape-cod
There 6 different types of food: apricot, cabbage, carrot, cherry, radish, cape-codmelon
There are 6 different nationalities: indian, chinese, british, american, indonesian, russian
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, bus, car, ship, subway, tram
 1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 2. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
 3. the colonial house is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
 4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the british##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating cape-codmelon is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the indian##1
 8. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the car is between the person eating radish and the american##2
10. the chinese is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
11. the indian is the person driving the tram##1
12. the person driving the car is on the right of the american##1
13. the british is on the right of the victorian house##1
14. the person driving the boat is the wooden house##1
15. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the tram and the person eating radish##2
16. the craftsman house is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| House    | wooden            | victorian     | cape-cod     | colonial     | craftsman      | cottage     |
| Food        | cape-codmelon     | carrot   | apricot   | radish      | cherry        | cabbage |
| Nationality         | indonesian | american | british | chinese | russian | indian   |
| Transport   | boat           | ship     | car       | subway      | bus           | tram    |

