.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-16::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: orange, yellow, turquise, lavender, black, chestnut
There are 6 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, lemonade, milk, tea, juice
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, gospel, metal, r&b, rock
6 different pets are kept: cat, fish, guinea-pig, hamster, horse, lizard
 1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 2. the fan of dubstep is the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of blues and the person drinking milk##2
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is the fan of r&b##1
11. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
13. the fan of metal is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
14. the person who likes black is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
15. the fan of dubstep is the person who likes chestnut##1
16. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person drinking lemonade and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2       |     3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Color         | yellow            | chestnut  | orange | turquise  | black  | lavender  |
| Beverage           | milk | juice | water   | soy-milk | tea    | lemonade   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel             | dubstep      | blues      | metal      | r&b        | rock    |
| Pet           | lizard             | fish         | horse      | cat        | guinea-pig | hamster |

