.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-17::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, trike, boat, scooter, car
The people have 6 different jobs:  accountant, analyst, chef, photographer, security-guard, carcher
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, family, martial-arts, mystery, thriller
6 different games are played: canasta, snooker, bridge, scrabble, mah-jongg, whist
 1. the person driving the car is between the person playing snooker and the person driving the tram##2
 2. the analyst is on the right of the carcher##1
 3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 4. the photographer is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person playing bridge is the security-guard##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person watching family movies is the security-guard##1
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person driving the scooter is the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
13. the analyst is on the far right##1
14. the analyst is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the chef##1
16. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
17. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |      3      |    4     |      5       |    6     |
| Transport      | tram          | car            | trike       | scooter | motorbike       | boat     |
| Job           | photographer | security-guard | accountant  | chef     | carcher      | analyst  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | family         | documentary | mystery  | martial-arts | thriller |
| Game         | whist     | bridge       | snooker     | mah-jongg    | canasta     | scrabble  |

