.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-18::.
There 6 different types of food: cauliflower, cherry, cranberry, lemon, pear, pepper
6 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, turtle, bird, hamster, cat
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: r&b, country, soul, hip-hop, blues, dubstep
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, lacrosse, rugby, sailing, swimming
 1. the owner of the mouse is between the fan of r&b and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 2. the person eating cherry is the fan of dubstep##1
 3. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 4. the fan of country is the person eating lemon##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is the person eating cranberry##1
10. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
12. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating pear##1
13. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the fan of country##1
14. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the fish##1
15. the owner of the turtle is the fan of blues##1
16. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |       3       |    4     |    5     |    6    |
| Food          | cauliflower | lemon        | cranberry     | pear     | pepper   | cherry  |
| Pet           | turtle       | cat | bird | hamster  | mouse | fish |
