.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-19::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, collecting, fishing, rock-climbing, skydiving, video-games
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, doctor, dressmaker, manager, pilot, teacher
City: san-francisco, rome, london, miami, edinburgh, venice
6 different games are played: go, billiard, poker, scrabble, monopoly, whist
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person playing go and the person traveling to rome##2
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 6. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the coach is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the teacher##1
12. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the doctor and the person playing scrabble##2
14. the person playing scrabble is the person traveling to venice##1
15. the person who's hobby is camping is the dressmaker##1
16. the pilot is on the right of the manager##1
17. the person traveling to rome is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |       4       |     5      |     6      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | video-games | skydiving | rock-climbing | collecting | camping    |
| Job           | coach     | teacher     | doctor    | manager       | pilot      | dressmaker |
| City   | rome | london       | miami | san-francisco       | venice       | edinburgh   |
| Game           | whist    | monopoly         | go       | poker         | scrabble     | billiard    |

