The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, country, disco, house, metal, trance
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, french, malaysian, polish, russian, spanish
6 different pets are kept: lizard, hedgehog, frog, rabbit, pony, ferret
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the russian##1
 2. the fan of disco is the owner of the pony##1
 3. the russian is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the argentine##1
 7. the malaysian is on the far left##1
 8. the malaysian is the fan of disco##1
 9. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of disco##1
10. the owner of the ferret is between the person who growsorchid and the owner of the rabbit##2
11. the owner of the rabbit is the polish##1
12. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
14. the fan of country is the russian##1
15. the fan of trance is on the right of the argentine##1
16. the french is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |      4      |     5     |    6     |
